metadata.name: Chrysalis Exclusive
metadata.description:
Chrysalis NFT 1 of 1750.
To purchase NFT, please go to the website https://cocoonmdv.com/my-account/

Chrysalis members will gain access to our one-of-kind lifestyle service offering expert advice in the Art of Science, Self-Care, and Luxury Services opening 2022 and our private wellness club located in the French Riviera due to open Summer 2024. boasting 15,000 to 20,000 square feet in size, access is capped to 1500 members.  

The first 10 token holders of Chrysalis will gain exclusive private access to the Cocoon Mode De Vie private members club twice a year for 1 week each time where Cocoon Wellness will bring the experts in wellbeing to you.

Members are required to log into Cocoonmdv.com to create a profile and register your wallet/token as proof of ownership
